     H            Y.
     F** AB#RSP *************************************************************
     F*  SERVICE PARTS LABEL PRINT                                          *
     F*       MIXED LOAD FOR NAPLD                                          *
     F****************************************** AB#R2C *********************
     FAB#PWSP CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FFCEPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFCEPL30 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAB#PP85 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAB#PL13 IF  E           K        DISK
     F                                              KINFDS @INFDA
     A*
     FAB#WP2Q O   E           K        DISK                           UC
      * SERIAL NUMBER FILE
     FAB#PP70 O   E                    DISK                      A
     FAB#NP30 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     FAB#PL76 UF  E           K        DISK
      * MASTER FILE
     FAB#PP66 O   E                    DISK
     E*****************************************************************
     E                    ER      1  14 60
     E                    CMD     1   1 30
     E                    MHN         8 20
     E                    TQY         8  7
     E                    PAC         8  3
     E                    PQY         8  5
     E                    MH@        16 20
     E                    TQ@        16  7
     E                    PA@        16  3
     E                    PQ@        16  5
     I*****************************************************************
     I@INFDA      DS
     I                                    B 397 4000@@RCD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60@@TIM
     I                                        1   20@@HH
     I                                        3   40@@MM
     I* INTERNAL PART NUMBER
     I* USER PART(AB#PP10)
     I            DS
     I                                        1  20 WMHIN
     I                                        1   5 BAMHN1
     I                                        6  10 BAMHN2
     I                                       11  15 BAMHN3
     I                                       16  20 BAMHN4
     I                                        1   7 WPA1
     I                                        8  12 WPA2
     I* GENERAL FASTNERS, HOLLINGSWORTH PART
     I            DS
     I                                        1  13 W#PA1
     I                                        2   8 WKPA1
     I* USER PART(AB#PP10) EDITED FOR DISPLAY
     I            DS
     I                                        1  23 @PART
     I                                        1   5 WAMHN1
     I                                        6   6 @P1
     I                                        7  11 WAMHN2
     I                                       12  12 @P2
     I                                       13  17 WAMHN3
     I                                       18  18 @P3
     I                                       19  23 WAMHN4
     I* SHIPPING DATE(DISPLAY)
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80PNOHZ
     I                                        1   40PNOYY
     I                                        3   40PNOY
     I                                        4   40PY
     I                                        5   60PNOMM
     I                                        7   80PNODD
     I* SHIPPING DATE(AB#WP2N MMDDYY)
     I            DS
     I                                        1   6 WKMDY
     I                                        1   20WKMDYM
     I                                        3   40WKMDYD
     I                                        5   60WKMDYY
      *
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 @SHIN
     I                                        1   5 @SHN1
     I                                        6  10 @SHN2
     I                                       11  12 @SHN3
     I* CHANGE DATE(FCEPL01)
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A2DATE
     I                                        1   40A2TRYY
     I                                        5   60A2TRMM
     I                                        7   80A2TRDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A2GSHZ
     I                                        1   40A2GSYY
     I                                        5   60A2GSMM
     I                                        7   80A2GSDD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A2SSHZ
     I                                        1   40A2SYYY
     I                                        5   60A2SYMM
     I                                        7   80A2SYDD
     I* LOCATION(FCEPL01)
     I            DS
     I                                        1   6 A2STKR
     I                                        1   1 A2STRK
     I                                        2   3 A2STRT
     I                                        4   5 A2STRR
     I                                        6   6 A2STRD
     I* LOCATION(FCEPL01)
     I            DS
     I                                        1   6 A2KTKR
     I                                        1   1 A2KTRK
     I                                        2   3 A2KTRT
     I                                        4   5 A2KTRR
     I                                        6   6 A2KTRD
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
     C***********************************************************************
     C* PARM                                                                *
     C***********************************************************************
     C* KEY1                                                                *
     C***********************************************************************
     C* FIXED ORDER FILE(AB#PL13)
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           WNONY
     C                     KFLD           PNOYY
     C                     KFLD           PNOMM
     C                     KFLD           PNODD
     C                     KFLD           PNUKE
     C* FIXED ORDER FILE(AB#PL13)
     C           KEY6      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           WNONY
     C                     KFLD           PNOYY
     C                     KFLD           PNOMM
     C                     KFLD           PNODD
     C                     KFLD           PNUKE
     C                     KFLD           WAMHN1
     C                     KFLD           WAMHN2
     C                     KFLD           WAMHN3
     C                     KFLD           WAMHN4
     C                     KFLD           WORDN
     C* PART MASTER(FCEPL01)
     C           KEY2      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           BASHN1
     C                     KFLD           BASHN2
     C                     KFLD           BASHN3
      *
     C***********************************************************
     C*
     C                     EXSR @INZ
B01  C           WKDSP     DOWNE'9'
     C           WKDSP     CASEQ'0'       @STRT
     C           WKDSP     CASEQ'1'       @MAIN
     C                     ENDCS
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     EXSR @END
     C***********************************************************
     C* @INZ:INITIALIZE WORK AREA
     C***********************************************************
     C           @INZ      BEGSR
     C*
     C                     MOVE '0'       WKDSP   1
     C                     MOVE *ALL'0'   WKBLAK 10
     C                     Z-ADD1         BIN
     C*
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    PNONY
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    PNKOJ
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    PNUKE
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     PNOHZ
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    PORD#
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN22
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C***********************************************************
     C* BARCODE ENTRY
     C***********************************************************
     C           @STRT     BEGSR
      *
     C                     EXFMTAB#PWSN0
      *
     C                     SELEC
     C           *INKI     WHEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE '1'       WKDSP
     C           *INKC     WHEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE '9'       WKDSP
     C                     OTHER
     C                     EXSR @CHK0
     C* CHECK OK?
     C           *IN30     IFEQ '0'
     C           *INKE     ANDEQ*ON
     C                     EXSR @ITEM
     C                     EXSR @WRT1
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN87
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D@BAR
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDSL
      *
     C                     ENDSR
     C***********************************************************
     C* BARCODE ENTRY
     C***********************************************************
     C           @CHK0     BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVEAWKBLAK    *IN,30
     C                     SETOF                     87
     C           D@BAR     CHAINAB#PL76              90
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *ON
     C                     SETON                     3031
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELPUNONY    PNONY
     C                     MOVELPUNKOJ    PNKOJ
     C                     MOVELPUNUKE    PNUKE
     C                     Z-ADDPUBINN    BIN
     C                     Z-ADDPUDAT     PNOHZ
     C                     MOVELPUODRN    PORD#
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     PULPDT
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     PUKODT
     C                     TIME           PUKOTN
     C                     MOVEL#USER     PUKOME
     C                     UPDATAB#PP751
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C***********************************************************
     C* @MAIN:CONTROL DISPLAY
     C***********************************************************
     C           @MAIN     BEGSR
     C*
     C                     EXFMTAB#PWSN2
     C* CLEAR MSG
     C                     MOVEAWKBLAK    *IN,30
     C                     SETOF                     87
     C*
     C                     SELEC
B02  C           *INKC     WHEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE '9'       WKDSP
     C*
     C           *INKL     WHEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE '0'       WKDSP
     C                     OTHER
     C                     EXSR @CHK1
      *
B03  C           *INKE     IFEQ '1'
     C* CHECK OK?
     C           *IN30     ANDEQ'0'
     C                     EXSR @ITEM
     C                     EXSR @WRT1
     C                     END
      *
     C                     ENDSL
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C***********************************************************
     C* # OF PARTS
     C***********************************************************
     C           @ITEM     BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     @ITM    30
     C                     MOVE PNONY     WNONY   40
      *
     C           KEY1      SETLLAB#PL13
     C           *IN93     DOUEQ*ON
     C           KEY1      READEAB#PL131                 93
     C           *IN93     IFEQ *OFF
     C           BASKJY    ANDEQ*BLANK
     C           PORD#     IFNE *BLANK
     C           PORD#     ANDNEBAODRN
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
     C           BIN       IFNE *ZERO
     C           BANOBN    ANDNEBIN
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
     C           PNUKE     IFNE *BLANK
     C           BANUKE    ANDNEPNUKE
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ADD  1         @ITM
      *
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     ENDSR
     C***********************************************************
     C* @CHK1:CHECK ITEMS ON 1ST. SCREEN
     C***********************************************************
     C           @CHK1     BEGSR
     C*
     C* DELIVERY CODE BLANK ?
     C           PNONY     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     3031
     C                     MOVELER,1      MSG
     C                     GOTO #CHK1
     C                     END
     C*
     C* FACTORY CODE BLANK ?
     C           PNKOJ     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     3032
     C                     MOVELER,2      MSG
     C                     GOTO #CHK1
     C                     END
     C*
     C* DOCK CODE BLANK ?
     C           PNUKE     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     3033
     C                     MOVELER,3      MSG
     C                     GOTO #CHK1
     C                     END
     C*
     C* SHIPPING DATE
     C           PNOHZ     IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     3034
     C                     MOVELER,4      MSG
     C                     GOTO #CHK1
     C                     END
      *
     C           PNOMM     IFLT 1
     C           PNOMM     ORGT 12
     C                     SETON                     3034
     C                     MOVELER,5      MSG
     C                     GOTO #CHK1
     C                     END
      *
     C           PNODD     IFLT 1
     C           PNODD     ORGT 31
     C                     SETON                     3034
     C                     MOVELER,5      MSG
     C                     GOTO #CHK1
     C                     END
     C*
     C* BIN       *
     C           BIN       IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     3035
     C                     MOVELER,6      MSG
     C                     GOTO #CHK1
     C                     END
     C*
     C*
     C           #CHK1     ENDSR
     C***********************************************************
     C* @WRT1:WRITE LABEL DATA
     C***********************************************************
     C           @WRT1     BEGSR
     C*
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     @@CNT   50
     C                     MOVE PNONY     WNONY   40
     C                     SETON                     87
      *
     C                     EXSR @OTHER
     C*
     C           #WRT1     ENDSR
     C***********************************************************
     C           @NMBR     BEGSR
     C***********************************************************
      *
     C                     MOVE *ALL'9'   @@14   140
     C           WNONY     CHAINAB#NP30              97
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     N3UDAT
     C                     TIME           N3UTIM
     C                     MOVEL#PGM      N3UPGM
     C                     MOVEL#USER     N3UUSR
     C                     MOVEL#WSID     N3UWIS
     C                     Z-ADDWNONY     N3NONY
     C           *IN97     IFEQ *ON
     C                     Z-ADD1         N3NMBR
     C                     WRITEAB#NP301
     C                     ELSE
     C                     ADD  1         N3NMBR
     C           N3NMBR    IFEQ @@14
     C                     Z-ADD1         N3NMBR
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     UPDATAB#NP301
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
     C***********************************************************
     C* @OTHER:OTHER DELIVERY LABEL
     C***********************************************************
     C           @OTHER    BEGSR
     C*
     C* SERVICE PART?
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN55
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    SRVF
     C           *IN22     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELCMD,1     P@CMD
     C                     Z-ADD30        P@LEN
     C                     CALL 'QCMDEXC' P#CMD          99
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN22
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     OPEN AB#WP2Q
     C*
     C  N88      KEY1      SETLLAB#PL131
     C  N88      KEY1      READEAB#PL131                 93
     C*
     C   88      KEY6      SETLLAB#PL131
     C   88      KEY6      READEAB#PL131                 93
B01  C           *IN93     DOWEQ'0'
     C           BASKJY    IFNE ' '
     C                     GOTO #READ3
     C                     END
     C*
     C* ORDER# SELECTED ?
     C           PORD#     IFNE *BLANK
     C           PORD#     IFNE BAODRN
     C                     GOTO #READ3
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C*
     C           BIN       IFNE BANOBN
     C                     GOTO #READ3
     C                     END
      *
     C                     CLEARAB#PP701
     C* GET PART NAME
     C*
     C           KEY2      CHAINFCEPL30              91
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *OFF
     C           F3GSKD    ANDEQ*BLANK
     C                     MOVELF3SMEI    I2PNAM           PART NAME
      *
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    I2PNAM
     C           KEY2      SETLLFCEPL011
     C           #PART7    TAG
     C           KEY2      READEFCEPL011                 91
B02  C           *IN91     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVELA2SMEI    I2PNAM           PART NAME
     C*
E02  C                     END
E02  C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     MOVELWMHIN     I2PART           PART
     C*
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    I2DUMY           DUMMY
     C                     MOVE PNONY     I2DELY           DELIVERY
     C                     MOVE PNKOJ     I2FACT           FACTORY
     C                     MOVE PNUKE     I2DOCK           DOCK
     C*
     C* READ KANBAN MASTER
     C                     Z-ADDBANOMM    KEY12
     C*
     C                     MOVE PNOHZ     I2SHDT           SHIP DATE
      *
     C*
B1   C           *IN88     IFEQ '1'
      *
     C                     DO   D@PLT
     C                     EXSR @NMBR
      *
     C                     MOVE N3NMBR    I2SERL
     C                     MOVELPNONY     I2SERL
     C                     EXSR #PP70
     C                     Z-ADDBASRYO    PIQTY
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    POQTY
     C                     CALL 'AB#R2K'  P2
     C                     MOVELPOQTY     I2CQTY           QTY
     C           @ITM      IFGT 1
     C                     MOVEL'0'       I2PART    P
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    I2CQTY
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     MOVE I2SERL    I2CASE
     C                     MOVEL'242'     I2CASE
     C                     WRITEAB#WP2Q1
      *
     C                     EXSR #P66
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     GOTO #READ3
     C*
     C                     ELSE
     C           @FLAG     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     GOTO #READ3
     C                     END
     C*
E2   C                     END
E1   C                     END
     C*
     C* USER ONLY MARKED
      *
      *
     C                     DO   D@PLT
     C                     EXSR @NMBR
      *
     C                     MOVE N3NMBR    I2SERL
     C                     MOVELPNONY     I2SERL
     C                     EXSR #PP70
     C                     Z-ADDBASRYO    PIQTY
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    POQTY
     C                     CALL 'AB#R2K'  P2
     C                     MOVELPOQTY     I2CQTY           QTY
     C           @ITM      IFGT 1
     C                     MOVEL'0'       I2PART    P
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    I2CQTY
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     MOVE I2SERL    I2CASE
     C                     MOVEL'242'     I2CASE
     C                     WRITEAB#WP2Q1
      *
     C                     EXSR #P66
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     END
      *
     C           #READ3    TAG
     C  N88      KEY1      READEAB#PL131                 93
     C   88      KEY6      READEAB#PL131                 93
     C                     END
      *
     C                     CLOSEAB#WP2Q
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C***********************************************************
     C* WRITE CASE DATA FOR 0323
     C***********************************************************
     C           #P66      BEGSR
      *
     C                     CLEARAB#PP661
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     A6KYMD
     C                     TIME           A6KTIM
     C                     MOVE BATOKU    A6TOKU
     C                     MOVE BANONY    A6NONY
     C                     MOVE BANKOJ    A6NKOJ
     C                     MOVE BANUKE    A6NUKE
     C                     MOVELI2CASE    A6MLBL
     C                     Z-ADDBANOHZ    A6NYMD
     C                     Z-ADDBANOBN    A6NBIN
      *
     C                     WRITEAB#PP661
      *
     C                     ENDSR
     C***********************************************************
      *  SET FIELDS FOR AB#PP70
     C***********************************************************
     C           #PP70     BEGSR
      *
     C***********          CLEARAB#PP701
     C                     Z-ADD*YEAR     EKKOYY
     C                     Z-ADD*MONTH    EKKOMM
     C                     Z-ADD*DAY      EKKODD
     C                     TIME           @@TIM
     C                     MOVE @@HH      EKKOHH
     C                     MOVE @@MM      EKKOMN
     C                     MOVEL#USER     EKKOME
     C                     MOVE BANONY    EKNONY
     C                     MOVE BANKOJ    EKNKOJ
     C                     MOVE BANUKE    EKNUKE
     C                     MOVE F3ZETI    EKZETI
     C           F3ZETI    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE A2ZETI    EKZETI
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE WSYS      EKSYOS
     C                     MOVE BAODRN    EKODRN
     C                     MOVE BASHN1    EKSHN1
     C                     MOVE BASHN2    EKSHN2
     C                     MOVE BASHN3    EKSHN3
     C                     MOVE BANOYY    EKNOYY
     C                     MOVE BANOMM    EKNOMM
     C                     MOVE BANODD    EKNODD
     C********             Z-ADD@@RCD     EKRCNO
     C                     Z-ADDBATOKU    EKTOKU
     C                     MOVELBAMHN1    EKMHN1
     C                     MOVELBAMHN2    EKMHN2
     C                     MOVELBAMHN3    EKMHN3
     C                     MOVELBAMHN4    EKMHN4
     C                     MOVE BANOBN    EKNOBN
     C                     MOVE N3NMBR    EKSERL
     C                     MOVELPNONY     EKSERL
     C                     Z-ADDBADEYY    EKRLYY
     C                     Z-ADDBADEMM    EKRLMM
     C                     Z-ADDBADEDD    EKRLDD
     C                     WRITEAB#PP701
      *
     C                     ENDSR
     C***********************************************************
     C* @END:
     C***********************************************************
     C           @END      BEGSR
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C***********************************************************
** ER
E-01 ENTER DELIVERY CODE.
E-02 ENTER FACTORY CODE.
E-03 ENTER DOCK CODE.
E-04 ENTER SHIPPING DATE.
E-05 DATE IS WRONG.
E-06 ENTER BIN.
E-07 ENTER BOTH SERIAL NUMBER FROM AND SERIAL NUMBER TO
E-08 PLEASE MARK AT LEAST 1 OPTION
E-09 THIS FROM,TO IS ONLY FOR ARVIN SANGO
E-10 THIS FROM,TO IS ONLY FOR TRW-KOYO
E-11 THIS FROM,TO IS ONLY FOR OTHERS
E-12 NO DATA IN ORDER FILE(AB#PP10)
E-13 YOU CAN NOT USE F7(DETAIL) KEY WITH SERIAL NUMBER
E-14 DO NOT USE THE NUMBER OF LABELS FOR ASI.PLEASE USE SERIAL #
**
CLRPFM AB#WP2Q
